description:
[b]Official presets can only publish FLomka, if someone puts out presets marked as CWAV, please inform me on Steam: FLomka or Discord: FLomka#0202. (Developed by RedFox)[/b]

[h1]Future Update[/h1]

Attention, we are discontinuing wallpaper support via Wallpaper Engine UI, 03/16/2021 we plan to completely abandon the internal interface, but maintain backward compatibility, it is also possible only temporarily. Complete redesign of elements and creation of a cool and convenient UI right in the browser. A converter will be created for existing presets.
At the moment, we have been collecting data from your presets for 6 months (no confidential data). From this moment on, new functionality is written only for the new CWAV-UI, without the possibility of using it in the current editor. We hope you get a new experience from what we have in mind.


You can always offer your improvements to us and we will certainly listen to you.
[url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/discussion/1509243786/2140840224668431912/]FaQ & Guide[/url]
Developed by RedFox Inc.
